The abbreviated day of the week Mon-Sun: The day since this research #2 started, with the initial day being day 1, its 21 days of research into how dieting that involves eating whatever as long as within the boundaries or confinements of following a diet that avoids meat, added butter, processed sweets, and alcohol, with the adden avoidance of gluten half way through, and also exercising with 20-30 minutes of cardio kickboxing on a standup boxing bag, followed by 18 exercises of weight training in 3 sets of 10-12 repetitions per exercise. And also lipocavitation on Mondays, Wednesdays, and Saturdays for 5 minutes each on the midsection abs and flanks at the sides, each upper arm, and each thigh.
